ly 0.6886 log loss\\n   - **10-game windows worse than 5-game**: Suggests recency matters\\n\\n3. **Ensemble performance**: LR + NN ensemble achieves 0.6269 log loss, matching the best previous result but not improving significantly on single LR.\\n\\n4. **Calibrati",\n  "eval_summary": "# Model Evaluation Report\\n\\n## Executive Summary\\n\\nAfter evaluating 15 completed experiments, I have a **PROMOTE** decision for the best performing model. Here\'s my comprehensive analysis:\\n\\n## 1. Experiment Rankings (by Log Loss)\\n\\n**Top 5 Models:**\\n1. **LR - ELO + Recent Form (5 games)** - Log Loss: 0.6264 \\u2b50\\n2. NN - ELO + Recent Form - Log Loss: 0.6268\\n3. Ensemble - LR + NN (ELO + Form Features) - Log Loss: 0.6269\\n4. Ensemble LR+NN - ELO Features Only - Log Loss: 0.6269\\n5. Logistic Regression Base"\n}\n```'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': [{'text': "I'll generate the comprehensive Predicto analysis report. Let me gather all the necessary data first.", 'type': 'text'}, {'id': 'toolu_017DyNJ6WQduYZSHLsGs4BsM', 'caller': {'type': 'direct'}, 'input': {}, 'name': 'get_all_experiment_summary', 'type': 'tool_use'}]}, {'role': 'user', 'content': [{'type': 'tool_result', 'tool_use_id': 'toolu_017DyNJ6WQduYZSHLsGs4BsM', 'content': '[\n  {\n    "name": "Ensemble - LR + NN (ELO + Form Features)",\n    "method": "ensemble(logistic_regression, neural_network)",\n    "log_loss": 0.626922,\n    "brier_score": 0.218312,\n    "accuracy": 0.6454,\n    "status": "completed"\n  },\n  {\n    "name": "NN - ELO + Recent Form",\n    "method": "neural_network",\n    "log_loss": 0.626805,\n    "brier_score": 0.218702,\n    "accuracy": 0.642,\n    "status": "completed"\n  },\n  {\n    "name": "LR - ELO + Recent Form (5 games)",\n    "method": "logistic_regression",\n    "log_loss": 0.62638,\n    "brier_score": 0.218493,\n    "accuracy": 0.644,\n    "status": "completed"\n  },\n  {\n    "name": "LR - ELO Features Only (Baseline)",\n    "method": "logistic_regression",\n    "log